"Charming Home on Birch Avenue in Spring Lake-28390"
Welcome to this delightful 4-bedroom, 2 1/2 bathroom home in the heart of Spring Lake.
This well-maintained property offers a cozy atmosphere, featuring a spacious living area, a modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances, and a lovely backyard perfect for outdoor gatherings.

Key Features:
- 4 Bedrooms, 2 1/2 Bathrooms 
- Modern Kitchen with Stainless Steel Appliances
- Spacious Living area
- Beautiful yard
- Sprinkler system in front and back yard
- Convenient Location in Spring Lake

This Home is situated in a convenient location, close to schools, parks, and all the amenities' Spring Lake has to offer. Don't miss  the opportunity to make this your new home.
